      <Run Tag="xhtml/part02chapter23.html#chapter23figure02">Figure 23.2. Defense&#x2019;s optimal mix.</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Margin="0,1,0,0" TextAlignment="Justify" FontFamily="times new roman" FontSize="14">
      <Run Tag="__158">&#xA0;</Run>
    </Paragraph>
